</strong>: Thank you, Mr Chair, for that clarification. Well, my point then is that the principal Act, which is being amended by this Act, taking into account the eight amendments that have already happened over that time, is relevant, I believe. And that is my contribution on that clause. Kia ora.</p><p class="IndentMarginalone">Clause 3 agreed to.</p></div></body>
